snippet.title: The Booty Creek Cheek FREAK Trailer
snippet.description:
Out 5/19. Only on http://patreon.com/puppetcombo

Have you heard the legend of the Booty Creek Cheek Freak? Many say he terrorizes the creek to this day

Conner & Gary planned on a relaxing weekend getaway but now they're in the fight of their lives to protect DEM CHEEKS from the FREAK

A shockingly arousing 80's campground slasher from the DERANGED mind behind BLOODWASH Jordan King

Starring Jay from the Kubz Scouts in his greatest role

And Produced by Puppy Wombo
